title: Zulu of Zulu Tattoo featured on A&E'sTattoo Fixation
Zelda Ocarina of Time BA any% Speed Run Segment 5
description:
Not much trouble with this segment. It's a nice follow up to the last one. 

I compared with Kazooie and we are pretty much dead even. He got hit by one flame and I had to pause and unpause to correctly set up the bombs and hookshot (I guess that's another advantage for GCN). 

Anyway, I was looking for areas to improve this segment but I didn't really see any mistakes. The first flame Dampe threw might have cost half a second, but unless someone can tell me something to improve by more than that, I'll probably just keep this one. 

Time: 4:24.467

title: My Rollercoaster Tycoon 2 Contest Entry: Iron Man (1st Place!)
description:
Watch in 480p, It REALLY helps!
The park is now available to download here:
http://www.mediafire.com/?6g7lc94f4vt7c
My entry to Freebird887's Contest.
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sUczHwA1Tiw&feature=player_embedded
EDIT: I won! I placed first in the contest. Check the above link to verify

Credit to:
Music:
"Hero Worship - The B-52's" (0:00-1:27)
"Iron Man - Black Sabbath" (1:27-4:40)
Recording: Hyperionics Hypercam 2
Editing: Sony Vegas 7.0
Font: "Bionic Comic" from http://www.1001freefonts.com
Intro Background: Google Images (Search "Iron Man")
Additional Scenery: UCES (User Created Expansion Set) Expansion Pack (Available for free download online)

This is my second contest video, and I must say that this contest was much harder. The contest called for a LIM launched coaster, and frankly, LIM Launch Coasters are the absolute hardest coaster for me to build. Since my LIM launch at my Extreme Heights was a space filler and my LIM at my Infernal Views was pretty bad too, so I had to build a new ride. When I was thinking about that ride, the concept of Iron man came to me, and all the potential I could get from using the UCES expansion pack by building my own park! So, I went to scenario editor and built a small 85x85 park and proceeded to turn it into a full on city. The park, named Steel City, is one of my favorite parks, and if I get enough requests from you guys, I will happily upload the empty scenario as well as the completed one. Since every single step of the design process from the scenario up was done by me, I also worked to make this ride truly awesome, and with that, I tried to make the park as much like a city as possible. I added subways and a light rail system, and even added residential districts, parks, and factories. But perhaps my favorite part of the park was Tony Stark's house, which the ride blasts through pretty quickly. The building was designed using images from the movie, and I'd say it came out pretty well.

Ride Info
IRON MAN
LIM Launched Rollercoaster

EXC: 9.51
INT: 9.81
NAU: 7.22
Max Speed: 59 mph
Average Speed: 21 mph
Ride Time: 2 minutes 59 seconds
Ride Length: 7533 feet
Max Positive Vertical G's: 3.70 G's
Max Negative Vertical G's: -1.98 G's
Max Lateral G's: 1.38 G's
Air Time: 11.88 seconds
Drops: 17
Highest drop: 98 ft
Inversions: 3

I already went over the history of this ride above, so this is merely the more in detail stuff. It took me only one in-game year to build the track for Iron Man, but that's not say I didn't tinker with it for a while. My initial design, however, was the highest rated. One could argue the ride spent me the entirety of the 16 in-game years I spent on the park, since the scenery was the central theme of the park more so than most of the rides, and as such it was built as I worked my way through the park. With a park this fancy, too, do you really have to ask me whether or not I had money at all? I used no money for this park, since, well, let's face it, the park didn't have many rides, so I would have trouble funding the park's scenery, and also, I'm lazy. The name is derived from the superhero Iron Man (In case you didn't guess). The songs chosen were Hero Worship and Iron Man. Iron Man was chosen for obvious reasons, but Hero Worship was chosen because I like it as an intro song, and I like the B-52's.

List of all Rides in the park (Since all are visible from the ride) (In order of appearance):
Inverted Vertical Shuttle Rollercoaster (Breakout)
Monorail (Steel City Light Rail)
Launched Freefall (Super Speedy Elevator)
Monorail (Subway Line B)
Ferris Wheel (Boardwalk Wheel)
Looping Rollercoaster (Typhoon)
Monorail (Subway Line A)
Vintage Cars (Central Park Tour)
Vintage Cars (Production Line)
Reverse Freefall Rollercoaster (Nitroglycerin)
Flying Saucers (Rooftop Saucers)
Bumper Cars (Heavy Traffic)
Go Karts (Steel City 300)
Twist (Rooftop Sweepers)
Launched Freefall (Apollo Tower)

If you have any questions about how I built this rollercoaster, how to build good rollercoasters, how to do amazing scenery jobs, how to make good videos, where to get the software I use, or how to use the software, please leave it in the comments section and I will answer it. Thanks a Lot!

description:
http://syllix.bandcamp.com

The music for Sonic & Knuckles - Hidden Palace Zone (also used for Lava Reef Zone 2) I think has to be one of my all time favourites for video game music.

I remastered this to work on my ear training and production skills. This is not a midi rip - everything was picked out by ear. title: SWTOR - Datacron Location Guide - Alderaan (Republic) Patch 1.2 Update
description:
Republic guide. Patch 1.2 update on Strength+3 update in description below!
Step-by-step instructions on how to get to the datacrons in Alderaan. If you are below 45, you will need a group to get the last datacron (Endurance +3) in the Heroic Area - King's Pass.
Basically the same spots for the Empire but with different taxi points.

Click on the timers below to go straight to the Datacron walk-through in the video.

0:16 Aim +4, X:1106, Y:79, The Juran Mountains
0:40 Presence +3, X:-81, Y:-268, The Glarus Valley
1:18 Willpower +3, X:-2508, Y:-427, The Glarus Valley (Castle Panteer)
Body types 3 and 4 will not be able to get through the crack in the door. You may need to go with someone with Body types 1 or 2, kill yourself outside and have your friend rez you inside...
2:05 Strength +4, X:2191, Y:-2020, Kaamos Territory
Can't climb up the ladder anymore. You will need the MGGS to get this datacron.
Click here to see how: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4zlqZPTNIKo
3:01 Endurance +3, X:2721, Y:2497, The Juran Mountains/King's Pass
You need to get a Red Detonite Actuator at a vendor in The Juran Mountains at (1880,1109).*** (I found an easier way to get to the vendor. Pls go here http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lq9j3wT-G-4 and go to 7:12 for the route. Also, you should buy the MGGS as well for the Green Matrix Shard datacron in Corellia later on)
Only ONE person in the group needs to have it tp blow up the rock wall by the datacron. Then you need to go through a heroic area full of L40 elites to get to the cave where the datacron is at.

Good Luck!

CLIP DESCRIPTION:
Ghostface Killer takes out Steven Stone (Patrick Warburton), the personal security guard to big shot actress Jennifer Jolie (Parker Posey).

FILM DESCRIPTION:
Wes Craven's Scream (1996) was a half-parody/half-tribute to the first wave of slasher films of the 1970s and 1980s, and since most of them spawned a large number of sequels, it's only appropriate that Craven and screenwriter Kevin Williamson produced a third installment of their Scream franchise. Sidney Prescott (Neve Campbell), traumatized by the brutal murders of her friends, has left her hometown of Woodsboro and is working in California as a crisis intervention counselor. Meanwhile, "Stab," the novel by Gale Weathers (Courtney Cox Arquette), is spawning a series of successful horror films, and as Stab 3: Return to Woodsboro is being filmed in Los Angeles, a lunatic has gotten his hands on a copy of the script, and is murdering the characters in the same order that they die in the movie. But predicting who will die next is not as simple as it might seem, since the producers have circulated three different screenplays, with different endings. In addition to Campbell and Cox-Arquette, David Arquette returns from the first two films as less-than-bright "Dewey" Riley; new members of the cast include Parker Posey, Patrick Dempsey, Scott Foley, and Jenny McCarthy. Kevin Williamson wrote the original story, but the screenplay was penned by Ehren Kruger.

title: Rednex - The Devil went down to Georgia
description:
Gran canzone in versione dance/birrocchia

The devil went down to Georgia, he was looking for a soul to steal.
He was in a bind 'cos he was way behind: he was willin' to make a deal.
When he came across this young man sawin' on a fiddle and playin' it hot.
And the devil jumped upon a hickory stump and said: "Boy let me tell you what:
"I bet you didn't know it, but I'm a fiddle player too.
"And if you'd care to take a dare, I'll make a bet with you.
"Now you play a pretty good fiddle, boy, but give the devil his due:
"I bet a fiddle of gold against your soul, 'cos I think I'm better than you."
The boy said: "My name's Johnny and it might be a sin,
"But I'll take your bet, your gonna regret, 'cos I'm the best that's ever been."

Johnny you rosin up your bow and play your fiddle hard.
'Cos hells broke loose in Georgia and the devil deals the cards.
And if you win you get this shiny fiddle made of gold.
But if you lose, the devil gets your soul.

The devil opened up his case and he said: "I'll start this show."
And fire flew from his fingertips as he rosined up his bow.
And he pulled the bow across his strings and it made an evil hiss.
Then a band of demons joined in and it sounded something like this.
When the devil finished, Johnny said: "Well you're pretty good ol' son.
"But sit down in that chair, right there, and let me show you how its done."

Fire on the mountain, run boys, run.
The devil's in the house of the risin' sun.
Chicken in the bread pan, pickin' out dough.
"Granny, does your dog bite?"
"No, child, no."

The devil bowed his head because he knew that he'd been beat.
He laid that golden fiddle on the ground at Johnny's feet.
Johnny said: "Devil just come on back if you ever want to try again.
"I told you once, you son of a gun, I'm the best that's ever been."

And he played fire on the mountain, run boys, run.
The devil's in the house of the risin' sun.
Chicken in the bread pan, now they're pickin' out dough.
"Granny, will your dog bite?"
"No, child, no."

title: Classic Game Room HD - S.T.A.L.K.E.R. CALL OF PRIPYAT for PC review
description: Classic Game Room HD reviews STALKER CALL OF PRIPYAT for PC from GSC Game World and Viva Media. This first person shooter style RPG adventure game is the sequel to the popular PC game S.T.A.L.K.E.R.  Play as a soldier dropped into the zone to find out what happened to 5 crashed helicopters in the future after a fiction second meltdown at Chernobyl. The zone is filled with mutants, paranormal activities, artifacts and dirtbags packed with machine guns. Fun! Plod around through the rain and complete side missions, collect weapons and buy armor and upgrades. Fans of other time consuming RPG adventures like Fallout 3 and Borderlands may want to give this game a try. While the environment in STALKER may be huge it is very bleak and kind of bland compared to some other games, but still packs a cool feel with some action and random encounters as you wander about. This CGR review of S.T.A.L.K.E.R. Call of Pripyat has gameplay from STALKER Call of Pripyat on PC showing PC game play on a gaming laptop using an ATI card playing Stalker Call of Pripyat. title: Synthogy Ivory II VST Demo - Steinway D Concert Grand - HD
tags: ['Piano (Musical Instrument)', 'Demo', 'VST', 'VSTi', 'Synthogy', 'Ivory', 'Ivory II', 'Steinway', 'Steinway D', 'Steinway D Grand Piano', 'Grand Pianos', 'Alain Chomik', 'CrusaderBeach', 'Falling Star', 'Kawaï', 'CA91', 'CA 91', 'Kawaï CA91', 'Digital Piano', 'Virtual Studio Technology', 'Piano Numérique', 'Steinway D-274']
description:
I decided to redo a series of demos based on virtual instruments I use. Here is the first : the Steinway D Grand Piano by Synthogy Ivory II. By the way, the music of the demo I play is based on a mix of my composition and an adaptation of a part of the song "Falling Star" composed by Andrian Webster an English Pianist known on Youtube as "CrusaderBeach" .

J'ai décidé de refaire une série de demos sur les instruments virtuels que j'utilise. Voici la première : le piano Steinway D Grand Piano de Synthogy Ivory II. En passant, la musique de la démo que je joue est basée sur un mélange de ma composition et d'une adaption d'une partie de la musique "Falling Stars" composé par Andrian Webster, un pianiste Anglais, connu sur Youtube sous le pseudo CrusaderBeach. 

Here the settings I used - Voici les réglages que j'ai utilisé :
Program :
  Extra Resonant 1
  Sustain Resonance: +2dB
  Sympathetic Resonance: +3dB
  Pedal Noise On: +2,5dB
  Synth Layer : Warm PCM, Synth Gain: -1,5dB
  Release Samples: On
  Soft Pedal Samples: On
Effects
  Equalization: On
  Low Shelf Gain: +1,5dB
  High Shelf Gain: +3dB
  Ambiance: On - Concert Hall

The rest of settings remains unchanged - Le reste des réglages sont restés inchangés.

title: World of Tanks - Brytyjskie czołgi #12 - Caernarvon
tags: ['Caenv', 'Tier', 'HT', 'WOT', 'wot', 'world of tanks', 'best mmo', 'golden joystick', 'wg', 'WG.net', 'wargaming.net', 'wargaming', 'nowe czołgi', 'british', 'czołgi brytyjskie', 'test server', 'serwer testowy', 'aktualizacja 8.1', 'wejsa8.1', 'patch8.1', '0.8.1', '8.1', 'susek', 'jak grać', 'gameplay', 'jak wyglądają', 'wyglad', 'ciężki', 'Caernarvon']
description:
Cześć, przed wami chaotyczna rozgrywka z czołgu ciężkiego 8 Tieru jakim bez wątpienia jest Caernarvon. Ciężko wymówić nazwę ale gra tym pojazdem bez wątpienia jest przyjemna. 

Co do filmiku, jest to najgorszy video zrobione przeze mnie ... :/
Czemu tak wyszło ? Chciałem zrobić każdy czołg, opisać go. No ale niestety wiecie jak jest. Nie zawsze wychodzi. Próbowałem przez 2h nagrać coś ale zawsze wrzucało mnie na 10 tiery i nie było żadnej gry. Coś jak na tym video. Z braku czasu i pomysłów zdecydowałem się zrobić coś takiego.

Ale co do czołgu. 1600 HP czyli całkiem niezła liczba HP, pancerz nie najtwardszy ale poodbija sporo od czołgów niższego tieru oraz z dystansu. Prędkość sporo lepsza od poprzednich czołgów czyli Churchilów i Black Princ'a. Największy problem tego czołgu to działo 226 penetracji i tylko 230 obrażeń. Jest celne to fakt, oraz jest szybkostrzelne. Ale każdy inny HT na tym tierze ma DMG koło 400. Więc to jest słabe bo szybkostrzelność nie zastąpi mocnego DMG.

Zapraszam :)

This 2001 Toyota Altezza AS 200 has a 6 cylinder 2 litre DOHC engine which delivers 160 BHP (Brake Horse Power) assisted by the 4 speed automatic transmission giving a fuel consumption rate of 11.6 Km per 1 litre of gas. A very popular and sort after sedan in NZ and around the world. With its sporty looks, stylish interior and trade mark Japanese handling it's no wonder these vehicles are so popular on our country roads and liked by all.

The Toyota Altezza is the Japanese variant of the European Lexus IS200. It has been available in Japan since 1998, at which time it received many accolades and won Japan's coveted Car of the Year award with its VVTi engines and Beams Tuning. In Japan, the car is produced in two forms, the Inline-6 DOHC 24v VVT AS200, and the more powerful RS200 - with an Inline-4 DOHC 16v VVTi engine

The AS200 more closely resembles the UK variant of the car - with its 6 cylinder engine and 160 bhp (with 4 speed auto box). A cheaper alternative to its 4 cylinder brother, it nonetheless offers an inexpensive way into owning a Toyota Badged Lexus.

"Impressive though the Lexus IS200 is, it is overshadowed by the japanese market Altezza" - Car Import Guide Feb/Mar 2001. The RS200 gives out an explosion of power, almost comparable to the Honda VTEC, feeling and souding like a race car as the variable valve gear starts. The interior is refined and sophisticated, with good looking dials, though the majority of Japanese market Altezzas are Z-Edition without the leather seats. The Toyota Altezza is very enjoyable to drive - particularly in 6 Speed RS200 form, with a race-feel engine and great build quality. If you are looking for an automatic, the Japanese version has the 5 Speed F1-Style gearshift which is also great fun to drive. The Altezza can be spotted by the 'A' badge on its front grille.

The mileage of this vehicle is AA certified and guaranteed.

Если у Вас когда-нибудь возникнет непреодолимое желание произвести перепланировку квартиры (путем демонтажа НЕ несущей межкомнатной перегородки из ГКЛ), Вы можете столкнуться с рядом серьезных проблем, одной из которых является большой перепад высоты потолка (из ГКЛ) между смежными помещениями.

Допустим, Вы демонтировали стену, тем самым объединив кухню с гостиной. На кухне, высота потолка составляет 2 метра 50 сантиметров, а в гостиной 2 метра 45 сантиметров. Естественно, возникает вопрос: Как выровнять потолок (устранить перепад высот в 5 см) с минимальными затратами?

Сделать это можно с помощью переделки всего потолка (в двух смежных помещениях), однако Вам потребуется закупить большое количество материала, а это существенным образом отразится на Вашем кошельке. Да и вообще, монтаж потолка из ГКЛ, дело утомительное, грязное и очень непростое.

Сейчас я покажу Вам один из вариантов визуального выравнивания потолка между помещениями, благодаря которому, Вы сможете сэкономить огромное количество денег, сил, нервов и времени.

title: Unstoppable lava a few feet from Hawaii homes (October 28, 2014)
description:
HONOLULU (AP) — Hawaii officials will make arrangements for those living in the path of a lava flow to watch the destruction of their homes.

That accommodation is being made to "provide for a means of closure," Hawaii County Civil Defense Director Darryl Oliveira said Monday. "You can only imagine the frustration as well as ... despair they're going through."

Dozens of residents have been told they might have to evacuate as lava from Kilauea heads toward their homes.

The lava was about 100 yards from a home Monday morning, officials said.

After weeks of fitful advancement, the lava crossed Apaa Street on Sunday in Pahoa Village, considered a main town of the Big Island's isolated and rural Puna district. It was getting dangerously close to Pahoa Village Road, which goes straight through downtown.

THE LATEST

The flow advanced about 275 yards from Sunday morning to Monday morning, moving northeast at about 10 to 15 yards per hour. At other times, the lava slowed to about 2 yards per hour or sped up to about 20 yards per hour, depending on topography, said Janet Babb, a spokeswoman for the Hawaiian Volcano Observatory.

Teams of scientists from the observatory were walking alongside the flow day and night to provide updates, she said. At 11:15 a.m. Monday, the flow front was 580 yards from Pahoa Village Road.

Officials closed the Pahoa Village Road between Apaa Street and Post Office Road to everyone except residents.

Those living downslope of the flow are under an evacuation advisory. Most residents have left or have made arrangements to go somewhere else if necessary. Oliveira said he doesn't anticipate having to issue a mandatory evacuation order.

The couple living in the house closest to the flow have left but have been returning periodically to gather belongings, Oliveira said. "They are out of the property and awaiting the events to unfold."

He estimated the lava could reach the house sometime Monday evening.

Apaa Street resident Imelda Raras, said she and her husband are ready to go to a friend's home if officials tell them they should leave.

"We are still praying," she said. "I hope our home will be spared."

SLOW CREEP

Scientists began warning the public about the lava on Aug. 22. At the time, residents were cleaning up from a tropical storm that made landfall over the Puna district, toppling trees and knocking out electricity.

The lava has advanced and slowed as residents waited and watched.

Kilauea volcano, one of the world's most active, has been erupting continuously since 1983.

This is not an eruption at the caldera, the things that make for stunning pictures as red lava spews from the mountaintop.

Decomposition of vegetation in the lava's path has created methane gas, which if it accumulates and is ignited by heat can cause a blast, Babb said.

"It's not a massive explosion," she said. "But it can dislodge rocks. It can hurl large rocks several feet."

WHO IS AT RISK?

Initially, the lava seemed headed for the Kaohe Homesteads, a widespread, sparsely populated subdivision in the Puna district.

It reached vacant lots in the subdivision before it stalled. It skirted the northeast corner of the subdivision and then headed toward Pahoa.

Pahoa has a small-town, quaint and historic charm, but it's "the only town in a commercial sense in lower Puna," said state Sen. Russell Ruderman, who represents Puna and runs a natural food store in Pahoa.

Because the lava could change direction, any community in Puna is at risk. Everyone in the district lives on the volcano. The lush, agricultural district is about a 30-minute drive from the coastal town of Hilo.

The lava that crossed Apaa Street is on the other end of the street from the Raras home, but they're bracing for the possibility the lava will spread or change directions.

COUNTRY-STYLE LIVING

Why would someone live on an active volcano? Unlike Honolulu, the state's biggest city on the island of Oahu, the Big Island's Puna region has affordable land and offers a more rural way of life.

Located on the island's southeast side, the area is made up of subdivisions that have unpaved roads of volcanic rock.

Many live off the grid on solar power and catchment water systems.

Residents know the risks as there are special insurance requirements to buy land in certain lava zones.

PREPARATIONS

Sporadic suspensions in the lava's movement gave emergency crews time to work on building alternate routes to town in the event the flow covers the main road and highway.

Crews near the leading edge have been wrapping power poles with concrete rings as a layer of protection from lava heat.

Officials worried that if lava crosses Highway 130, it would isolate Puna from the rest of the island.

"Puna will be divided into the north side of the flow and the south side of the flow," Ruderman said.

description:

http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ilmyvvCXCyo Slow Motion (Hip-Hop/Pop/R&B Beat) [Prod. By Interkidd] background music. nice too. check these s guys out there nice In what is the latest release for Call of Duty series developer Infinity Ward, Modern Warfare 2 (MW2) is a great achievement that improves on the already stellar aspects of the first Modern Warfare. The first direct sequel in a series that previously only dealt with discontinuous stories on the frontlines in WWII, MW2 continues the setting of modern and authentic warfare, and is every bit as compelling as the original.

There are 3 different modes in the game: the Single-player storyline, Spec Op missions, and multiplayer. The storyline continues 5 years after the events of Modern Warfare 1, circa 2016. Despite the U.S. and U.K.s victory over Russian Ultranationalist leader Imran Zakhaev in the Second Russian Civil War, the war culminates with ultranationalist forces taking over the Russian Federation.

Tensions are at an all-time high and as U.S. General Shepard bluntly puts it today frontlines are historyThe war rages everywhere Things take a turn for the worse when Vladimir Makarov, who was one of Zakhaevs top lieutenants, stages a bloody false flag attack on Russia, leading to all out war.

Players command 4 different players throughout the story, from locations like Afghanistan, to Washington D.C., and must battle to repel the forces of Russia, Makarov, and more.

Despite the single players relatively short length, it is a very fun and solid experience that hits all the important points of FPS campaign modes. The action is fast, the script is intense, and the different missions have plenty of variety. The story carries enough of a unique blend of authenticity and show stopping moments to be better than your average FPS story.

If you dont find storytelling to be your thing, the completely new Special Op mode provides 23 one-of-a-kind challenging missions to complete. Whether you are holding off dozens of enemy foot soldiers with a Predator drone, racing through mountains in Kazakhstan on a snow mobile, sneaking through the radioactive wasteland near Chernobyl, destroying all cars on a bridge, or eliminating 10 heavily armored Juggernauts using just explosives and a knife, there is no shortage of excitement to be found.

The only problem is that there are not more of them, but achieving all 69 stars in this mode will take plenty of time, and you are always encouraged to reduce your completion time for each mission. Co-op is available both online and in person for Special Ops, which not only makes some of the missions easier, but adds the of fun that comes with playing with another person.

Finally, there is MW 2s multiplayer. Considered to be one of the centerpieces of the first Modern Warfare, the multiplayer here continues the excellent tradition of bringing variety, competitiveness, and depth into the picture, while still being a blast to play.

The different multiplayer modes combine a variety of team and individual deathmatchs, and objective based games. Like MW1, there is a system of perks, experience, and levels where new classes, weapons, and abilities can be unlocked. Although there have been accusations of balancing issues as well as some outrageous glitches and exploits, this reviewer has found no significant problems while playing online. Overall, while the experience is not highly differentiated from MW1, the new features, weapons, and maps make it all more than worth it.

While no major innovation or ground is broken in Modern Warfare 2, and some might consider it a bit too similar to the first game, it remains an excellent FPS with enough value and memorable moments. It is well worth playing for fans of the Call of Duty series and of FPSs in general.

All 3 game modes deliver very well, and there is enough value present to keep gamers busy for a long time, at least until Infinity Ward releases its Vietnam Call of Duty game in November this year.

description:
ก๋วยเตี๋ยวราดหน้าเนื้อสับ

ก๋วยเตี๋ยวราดหน้าเนื้อสับ (ก๋วยเตี๋ยวเนื้อสับ) อาหารจานเดียวที่ทำได้ไม่ยาก และใช้เครื่องปรุงไม่เยอะ ความอร่อยของเนื้อสับกับหอมใหญ่และมะเขือเทศ ทำเป็นน้ำราดรสชาติกลมกล่อม ราดลงบนเส้นใหญ่ที่เหนียวนุ่ม ทานคู่กับผักกาดหอม จานนี้ได้ทั้งความอร่อยและสารอาหารที่ครบถ้วนครับ 

http://www.foodtravel.tv/recipe.aspx?viewid=1101

Ingredient and How to cook, Please visit our English website.

http://en.foodtravel.tv/recfoodShow_Detail.aspx?viewId=743

วัตถุดิบก๋วยเตี๋ยวราดหน้าเนื้อสับ (ก๋วยเตี๋ยวเนื้อสับ)

1. เส้นใหญ่ 1/2 กิโลกรัม
2. เนื้อบด 1/2 กิโลกรัม
3. หอมใหญ่ (หั่นเป็นลูกเต๋า) 1/2 ถ้วย
4. มะเขือเทศ (หั่นเป็นลูกเต๋า) 1/2 ถ้วย
5. กระเทียม (สับละเอียด) 1 ช้อนชา
6. ซอสปรุงรส 1 ช้อนโต๊ะ
7. น้ำปลา 1 ช้อนโต๊ะ
8. น้ำตาล 2 ช้อนชา
9. แป้งมัน (ละลายน้ำ) 1-2 ช้อนโต๊ะ
10. ผักกาดหอม (หั่นเป็นท่อน)

อุปกรณ์ที่ใช้

กระทะ

วิธีทำก๋วยเตี๋ยวราดหน้าเนื้อสับ (ก๋วยเตี๋ยวเนื้อสับ)

1.  เส้นใหญ่ ผัดในน้ำมันเล็กน้อย อาจใส่ซีอิ๊วขาวเล็กน้อย (หรือไม่ใส่ก็ได้) หรือจะให้ลวกน้ำร้อน สะเด็ดน้ำพักไว้
2. กะทะใส่น้ำมัน ตั้งไฟกลาง ใส่กระเทียมสับเจียวพอเหลือง ใส่หอมใหญ่ ผัดพอสุก ใส่เนื้อผัดให้สุก ใส่มะเขือเทศ คลุกเล็กน้อย ปรุงรส ใส่น้ำพอท่วมปริ่มตัวเนื้อ พอเดือดใส่แป้งมันละลายน้ำ ดูให้น้ำข้นเหนียว ปิดไฟ
3. จานวางผักกาดหอมสับ วางเส้นใหญ่(ผัดหรือลวกแล้ว) ราดด้วยหน้าเนื้อที่ผัดไว้

tags: ['Suntory', 'Collection', 'Dirk', 'Planting', 'TEMARI', 'CHERRY', 'RED', 'Temari® Patio Verbenas', 'how-to-plant', 'planting instructions', 'low maintenance', 'easy-to-grow', 'continuous flowering', 'upright habit', 'containers', 'window boxes', 'hanging baskets', 'bedding plant', 'annuals', 'garden', 'Elizabeth Elan', 'Suntory Collection', 'Briana Vargas', 'Armstrong Garden Center']
description: In just a few easy steps, you too can enjoy the magnificence of Temari® Patio Verbenas anywhere in your home or garden! Begin first by using a high quality potting mix that will provide the plant good aeration, drainage and moisture retention. Fill your container will soil and arrange the plants in a such a way that allows them room for growth, first making sure to disturb the roots before placing them. Water immediately after planting, and once established, plan to water a few times per week, depending on the temperature. Temari ®Verbenas prefer locations in full sun, with high heat and require virtually no maintenance. Their gorgeous upright, large flowered growing habit compliments a variety of areas, and can be used in containers, window boxes, hanging baskets or even as a bedding plant. After just one month, look at the difference! With color all season long, you can't go wrong with the Temari® Patio Verbenas by the Suntory Collection. Presented by Elizabeth Elan from the Suntory Collection and Briana Vargas from Armstrong Garden Center.

title: Okami (PS2) Boss #13 - Lechku and Nechku
description:
Skip ahead to 1:10 to bypass the dialog if you want.
The 13th fight is against the Gold and Silver Demons, Lechku and Nechku. This strategy is based on using Amaterasu's powered up Thunder Edge as a main weapon and powered up Eighth Wonder as the secondary (and the skill that increases damage when two Glaives are equipped). As with my other boss videos, my strategy isn't absolute and I wouldn't mind other effective strategies or advice posted as comments.

The last video against Nechku sort of gave you a taste of what to expect in this fight.  Now you're in for some fun. The trick to bringing these guys down is to hit their attacks back at them until they're stunned. However they have quite an array of attacks. You can power slash all of the attacks except the ice shards, the bombs and the flower bud. Dodge the shards, use Inferno or Fireburst on the bomb, and Bloom the bud for some extra health. Lechku (the brown colored one) will hold up a sword once in a while which you should use Thunderbolt on. You'll have to explode the bombs Nechku uses and Power Slash the brown looking thing Lechku uses while it's over their heads or as close to them as possible. Once in a while they'll do a divebomb attack which can be avoided with a well used sidestep but the real damage it does is screw up the camera angle.  Anyways once you've hit back enough of their projectiles, one will get stunned and Oki will run back towards Ammy and offer himself to be used as an arrow.  Get close to Oki and hold the triangle until Oki has been fully loaded and cocked back onto the bow. Let him fly!  After Oki has been shot out and is clawing away, you need to double jump and knock the demon down and out.  You'll now have a few seconds to do some major damage before you have to repeat the whole grounding process again. Use Steel Fist Sake to do more damage or Vengence Slips if you're having problems.

So far this is my favorite fight in the game.

title: Ruislip Lido Railway | The Early Days
description:
A short montage of footage taken from the early days of the Society, with video from the 80s and 90s.

Over the next few years, we aim to create a new video for the railway, telling the story of the Ruislip Lido Railway and showing you around behind the scenes and the railway today. Still a little way off but footage such as the above would feature.

Hello everyone! After five sickening hours of searching, trading, and non-stop breeding, I gladly welcome you to my first Pokemon X and Y giveaway! The video obviously does most of the explaining, but I'll recite the idea behind this giveaway down here once more for those who need another reminder. 

I've been able to collect an egg for every single starter Pokemon out there, for all six generations. I thought it would be fun to do a giveaway, yet give it an interesting twist so it wasn't so generic. So, each winner will receive an egg containing a starter from the region they entered for, yet the starter they receive will be a complete surprise! If someone entered for Hoenn and won, they would receive an egg containing Torchic, Mudkip, or Treeko, but wouldn't know which one until it hatched.

title: The Cheltenham Flyer with 5043 Earl of Mount Edgcumbe
description:
The Cheltenham Flyer arguably the most famed named train on the GWR. The title became famed in the 1930's gaining record times running non-stop from Swindon to Paddington at average speeds of over 70 to 80mph over a 77 mile journey. The 'Flyer' had not ran non-stop since untill May 11th 2013. 5043 Earl of Mount Edgcumbe had the role of honor in re-running this historic train as well as carrying the famous Cheltenham Flyer square headboard. The run also marked the end of an era to the Great Western Mainline, with the clock now ticking the line is in full swing for modernisation and electrification, which will ultimately radically change Brunel's railway forever, and will never be the same again.
For this run as it was a non-stop working in both directions only two locations had to be chosen so I personally chose Sonning Cutting and Maidenhead Bridge, as they are the earliest iconic structures on the Great Western right from the beginning dating back to the late 1830's, I felt it would be a fitting, fulfilling and symbolic finale to capture the run on these locations for the last time, before they get destroyed forever by the overhead electrification.

At Sonning Cutting two western generations meet side by side before the HST overtakes steam, 5043 is seen carrying the iconic Cheltenham Flyer square headboard as it passes through the cutting. A few hours later on the return working 5043 fly's over Maidenhead bridge running 15 minutes early and very nearly catching me out there! And after that it was done. The rest is all but history, we can only see the GWML become electrified as time fly's by.

With thanks to Vintage Trains, West Coast Railways, First Great Western and Network Rail for making this miracle run happen 

These shots along with some others will be seen in MAINLINE DIARY 2013: PART 1 See http://www.ovpsteam.co.uk for more details

איך להכין מיץ סירופ "אומה"! מיץ שזיפים ירוקות יפני!
tags: ['איך להכין', 'איך להכין אומה', 'איך להכין מיץ', 'שתייה', 'משקאות ביפן', "אירה צ'אן", 'אתגר הירוק', 'אוכלים ירוק']
description:
הפעם אני אראה לכם איך להכין מיץ ״אומה״, אחד המיצים האהובים אליי ביפן. משקה מרענן ונהדר לקיץ שהוא די קל להכמנה אם יש לכם את כל המרכיבים הנכונים.

מרכיבים:
 - פירות אומה (פרי ירוק ממשפחת שזיפים) 2 קילו.
-מגבות נייר מטבח.
-מקלות חדות (רק מעץ).
-ליקר לבן (אלכהול).
-צנצנת גדולה 5 ליטר.
-שקיות
-סוכר גיבשים גדולים.

 הוראות הכנה:

חלק 1:
מנגבים את הפרי מאבק ומוצאים את החלק השחור מהפרי עם המקל (עשוי רק מעץ).
אחרי זה מחוררים 10 פעמים את הפרי ושמים בשקית.
אחרי כל התהליך של הנקיונות וחירורים, שמים את כל הפירות בתוך שקית ומוצאים מהשקית את האוויר ושמים במקפיא לילה שלם עד שהכל קפוא.

חלק2:
יום אחרי שהכל קפא, שמים בתוך הצנצנת (5 ליטר) שכבה של ״אומה״ ושכבה של גבישי סוכר עד סוף הצנצנת. אחרי זה שופכים את הליקר הלבן(אלכהול) שיחטא את הכל(לא לשים יותא מדי), משאירים קצת מקום אוויר בצנצנת.
סוגרים את צנצנת ושמים אותה במקום מוצל בלי אור לכמה חודשים עד שהכל נהפך לנוזל ליקר.
כל התהליך הכנה לוקח יומים. בשביל לשמור אל הצנצנת מומלץ לשים אותו במקום מוצל ולהשכיב אותו בהלכסון, פשוט תשימו אותו בקופסאת קרטון ושימו כרית. אחרי כמה חודשים הליקר יהיה בצבע אחר קצת ירוק כהה כזה, וכמה שיותר חודשים עובר הטעם שלו יהיה יותר טעים.

title: Anwendungsfilm: ROMPOX 1009 Airless Spritzverfahren, ROMEX GmbH
description:
Airless Spritzverfahren

ROMEX Beschichtungen und Versiegelungen mit dem zeit- und geldsparenden Airless-Spritzverfahren für Boden, Wand und Decke.  Der Faktor Zeit spielt auf vielen Baustellen eine große Rolle. Die Arbeiten müssen in meist viel zu kurzer Zeit fertig gestellt sein und die Beschichtungen ein perfektes Erscheinungsbild und optimale Eigenschaften vorweisen. Durch die Beschichtung mit dem Airless-Spritzverfahren können diese Anforderungen nun noch besser erfüllt werden. 
ROMPOX® 1009 Dampfdiffusionsoffene Versiegelung wird in diesem Verfahren für dünne Beschichtungen eingesetzt. Böden, Wände, Decken und verwinkelte Räume lassen sich auf diese Weise einfach und effizient beschichten. ROMPOX® 1009 Dampfdiffusionsoffene Versiegelung ist hervorragend für zementgebundene Untergründe mit rückwärtiger Durchfeuchtung geeignet. Aufgrund der guten Wasserdampfdurchlässigkeit ist sie auch für Magnesit- und Anhydritestriche geeignet sowie als Versiegelung von Hartgussasphalt in Innenräumen einsetzbar.

Einsatzbereiche
- Stadiontribünen, Reinräume, Garagen, Laboratorien...
- Beton- und Stahlflächen

- zementgebundene Untergründe mit rückwärtiger Durchfeuchtung
- dampfdiffusionsoffen
- Magnesit- und Anhydritestriche
- Hartgussasphalt in Innenräumen

Eigenschaften
- dampfdiffusionsoffen

- erfüllt Brandklasse B1 (schwer entflammbar)
- einfache Anwendung, schnelle Trocknung
- für Innen- und Außenbereiche
- für erdberührte Flächen geeignet
- Rutschhemmung durch Quarzsand oder Glasperleneinstreuung möglich
- geringer Materialverbrauch
- optimal für schwer zugängliche oder verwinkelte Bereiche

title: A Short Striper Fishing After Work in Lake Anna - Jan 4, 2014
description:
Fished for stripers between 2:30pm and 5:30pm.  It was the first cold day this winter.  I had limited number of jigs and lures inside the hatch.  But somehow the hatch was frozen stuck.  I delayed the launch until I opened the hatch.  Luckily I carried a can of deicer in the one of the utility boxes.

For an hour, I didn't see any fish images on the fish finder.   But once I saw stripers on the fish finder, I was able to catch 7 stripers for the next 2 hours.  At 5:30pm it became dark and cold

The water by Dike 3 was 49-52F.  I hoped the water becomes colder and more stripers show up next week

description:
http://www.tirzah-quartet.be

Tirzah-Quartet plays an arrangement of "The Rain Horse" live, while the animation movie The Rain Horse is screened.  Part of Filmworks XIX - The Rain Horse, by John Zorn.
Eva Vermeeren violin, Herlinde Verheyden cello, Karen Peeters harp, Jan Van de Perre, bass (arr).

Tirzah-Quartet is a new dynamic ensemble from Belgium that celebrates John Zorn's beautiful soundtrack-music, arranged for a chamber ensemble of Violin, Harp, Cello and Guitar/Bass and played by classicaly-trained musicians : Eva, Herlinde, Karen and Jan.  

Encouraged by the composer, Tirzah developed a heart-warming concert-program that combines Zorn's music with narration and the screening of a short animation-movie. This makes our concerts a memorable experience ! 

When Zorn received the 'Magister' title of Ghent University in 2011, Tirzah was invited to play at the Ceremony.

Tirzah played to great acclaim at Gent-Jazz : Zorn at 60 !

title: POR TI DOY TODO - JADITH MUEGUES (CAPE MEDINA) - Riohacha pnm
description:
Prsentacion en el marco del Festival Francisco el Hombre de Riohacha. Acordeon Walter Muegues. para contacto Jadith 312 6678991 - 316 5051806.
Por otro lado, hay una mujer en el grupo de los 12 seleccionados para el concurso. Se trata de Jadith Muegues, que canta vallenato desde los 14 años. Muegues se ha presentado en numerosos festivales compitiendo en las categorías de canción inédita y ahora lidera una agrupación mixta, Luna Vallenata.
 
Su motivación para participar fue diferente: "Quiero romper el estigma de que las mujeres no cantan vallenato -dijo-. Quiero mostrarle a la gente que tengo la capacidad de cantarlo, porque poseo esa fortaleza, esa voz fuerte y la cadencia que se necesita para cantar vallenato". Muegues, que en varias ocasiones ha sido la única mujer entre competencias de voces vallenatas, afirma que esa situación no se le ha hecho difícil. Porque si ha grabado discos es porque la gente que la ha oído se lo ha pedido. "Mi voz no es chillona, se adapta para cantar vallenato en todos sus matices, así que puedo interpretar todos los aires. Esta es la oportunidad para mostrar mi grupo y abrirme puertas", concluye

title: The 12 Supernatural Days of Christmas!
description:
MERRY CHRISTMAS!!!!
So once again the Roadhouse took something so simple and blew it WAAAAYYY out of proportion lol. Temi started it all by mentioning that we needed to write a supernatural version of the 12 days of Christmas.  Next thing we knew, we were planning a chorus, recording and making a video to match. The special thing about this chorus is it's sung by fangirls from all over the world. Three of us are from all over the US. The two others are from the UK. We've never met in real life. But we didn't let the distance keep us from doing this. Garra came up with the idea to record over one another one at a time and after many microphone/uploading/techincal-difficulties this was the finished recording lol.  We hope you enjoy it, and on behalf of the Gaia Online Roadhouse guild, I'd like to wish all the fellow SPN fans a Merry Christmas, happy holidays, and a scary new year =)

Some notes:
- This video/song took weeks to create
- The four horsemen parts were BITCH lol seeing as we've only seen one horseman so far. Though I did include some reapers in there for death, the starved corpses for famine, and croatoan scenes for conquest.
- The song used in the credits is "Carol of the Bells" by the Bird and the Bee
- You can check out the actual guild on gaiaonline.com, look for the roadhouse supernatural guild and drop in some time! Join the insanity lol =)

EDIT:
Sorry, have no clue why this song has like 3 minutes of dead space at the end... must have been a glitch or something *facepalm*

title: Jeep Wrangler doors seized? How to free doors & remove Part 1
tags: ['Jeep Wrangler', 'Unlimited', '4x4', 'JK', 'TJ', 'YJ', 'LJ', 'CJ', '4 door', 'doors', 'remove', 'removal', 'seized', 'free', 'stuck', 'Four-wheel Drive (Driveline)', 'How-to (Conference Subject)', 'off road', 'off roading', 'mud', 'unstick', 'nitto', 'toyo', 'mud grapplers', 'trail grapplers', 'Jeep wrangler automobile', 'remove jeep doors']
description:
If your doors on your Jeep Wrangler have been seized and not coming off, here's a few videos that I happen to throw together at the last minute when I finally dedicated a day to removing the door no matter what it took.

I'm guessing the previous owner of my Wrangler JK had never removed the doors. These doors were stuck on the Jeep like no other. Even the jack that I used took some time to free the doors on a few of them. 

At times while jacking the doors it may feel like the doors wont come and you're putting a ton of pressure on the door. Almost like the door will cave before the door will come off. A few pointers that I can give from my experience here is pump 1 time with the jack very slowly. If you're able to wiggle the door back and forth while you do it or just do one slow pump, then wiggle or shake the door back and forth for about 10 - 20 seconds or so to make sure the door is coming out to it's full potential before doing another single pump with the jack. Another thing, keep the jack as close as possible to the jeep near the blunt part of the curvature of the door. That's where the door is thickest and strongest. You will be least likely to bend or dent the door while lifting it with the jack. Don't forget to pad the jack where it makes contact with the door with something thicker / wider / longer to spread the pressure out and maximize it's contact patch. Lastly, be determined. You may feel as though you'll want to give up before that door comes off cause it will feel like you'll damage your door. Don't give in. Keep going at it. Them doors will come off. Just keep spraying with a lubricant to try to help it out as much as possible. There's nothing like driving around the city or the country side doorless and topless. It's a very neat experience and you get a ton of people looking and pointing at your Jeep!

Another recommendation I might add. Before putting your doors back on, put Anti-Seize on the small columns (can't think of a proper word right now - hinges??) that slide into the sleezes on the Jeep. The Anti-Seize will keep the doors from freezing on the Jeep again so next time you remove the doors, they will lift off without any problems and makes removal a breeze. Just apply some each time before you put the doors back on the Jeep.

Any questions just ask! Don't give up! Good luck and happy Jeepin!

title: Whistling Clan Line, and the great stampede at horse bend
tags: ['horses', 'stampede', 'surrey', 'clan line', '35028', 'merchant navy', 'surrey hills', 'albury common', 'steam train', 'vsoe', 'british pullman', 'pullman', 'whistle.', 'United Kingdom (Country)']
description: BR Merchant Navy Class 4-6-2 no 35028 Clan Line doing duty on its regular route round the Surrey hills, pulling the VSOE British Pullman, although unusually its has no diesel support on the back, which makes a pleasant change and is sporting a new previously unseen headboard.  The shot starts off normally at West Byfleet, and then I shoot off to catch it further round the route at a nice rural spot I had previously staked out, with a view over a field of well behaved calm horses. Didn't take into account the horses would be spooked, who all headed for me as if I could save them, and when I didn't they all hooved it off in front of the camera. Made for a good video.

tags: ['scion', 'hpi', 'hpi racing', 'scion fr-s', 'scion frs', 'frs rc', 'rc car', 'rc race', 'scion frs cup', 'frs cup', 'remote controlled car', '2012 frs cup', 'fr-s cup', 'scion hpi']
description:
The first ever Scion FR-S Cup, presented in collaboration with HPI Racing, took place at Toyota Headquarters on November 17th, 2012.  Over 100 competitors pitted their Scion FR-S RC cars against one another across three different skill classes.  In addition to the races, there was representation for some great vendors, such as Five Axis, OEM Audio +, Beat-Sonic and more.  Watch the video for some highlights from the event. Scion

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/scion
Twitter: https://twitter.com/scion
Instagram: http://instagram.com/scion
Google+: https://plus.google.com/+scion/posts
 
Scion is a brand of vehicles produced by Toyota Motor Corporation for the North American market. Founded in 2002, Scion was introduced at the New York Auto Show to appeal to Generation Y consumers. The first Scion models, the xA hatchback and xB wagon, went on sale in California in 2003, followed by a sports coupe, the tC, and a nationwide U.S. launch in 2004.

A successor to the xA, the xD, premiered in 2008, and the Scion marque expanded to Canada in 2010.  Scion currently has five models: the tC, xB, iQ, xD, and the FR-S. The Scion name, meaning the descendant of a family or heir, refers both to the brand's cars and their owners.

title: حادثة ماجد ناصر وجمهور الوصل
description:
انطلق مشجع وصلاوي بعد صافرة نهاية المباراة التي خسرها فريقه الإمبراطور أمام الاهلي 4-صفر في ختام الجولة 16 من دوري "اتصالات" للمحترفين بكرة القدم، مسرعا باتجاه حارس الفرسان ماجد ناصر ورمى وشاح النادي بوجه الحارس الذي قابله بابتسامة.
 
وواجه ناصر أيضا باعصاب هادية مشجعا وصلاويا آخر اقتحم الملعب وتحدث معه بغضب رغم أن ماجد معروف عنه العصبية الزائدة خلال المباريات في مواقف مشابهة.
 
وصرح ماجد ناصر لقناة أبوظبي الرياضية بعد المبارة، أنه لا ينوي رفع دعوى قضائية على المشجعين اللذين اقتحما الملعب من أجل مواجهته.
 
وكان ماجد ناصر الذي انتقل من الوصل إلى الأهلي في أكتوبر الماضي في ظروف صعبة نهاية فترة إيقافه 17 مباراة، قد واجه في مباراة الديربي التي تعد الأولى للفريقين منذ انتقاله صافرات الاستهجان إثر قيامه بالاحتفال بأهداف فريقه الأهلي الأربعة خاصة الهدف الثاني.
 
ولاقت هذه الحادثة ردود فعل واسعة في الشارع الرياضي الإماراتي، وأحدثت ضجة في وسائل التواصل الاجتماعي وأجهزة "بلاك بيري"، وعبرت الكثير من جماهير الوصل عن غضبها لاحتفال ماجد ناصر أمام فريقه السابق بـ "طريقة مبالغة"، مؤكدة أنه كان عليه احترام فريقه السابق "الذي قدم له الكثير من الدعم وصنع منه اللاعب الذي هو عليه حاليا"، على حد تعبيرها.

تصوير: إبراهيم شكرالله
تحرير الفيديو: ميثم الأنباري

title: An ihrer Seite - Trailer
description:
Kann man loslassen, was man am meisten liebt?

Seit 50 Jahren sind Fiona (Oscar®-Gewinnerin Julie Christie) und Grant (Gordon Pinsent) verheiratet; seine vereinzelten Seitensprünge sind Jahrzehnte her und Fiona hat ihm verziehen. Gelegentlich macht sie noch Andeutungen, die für Spannungen sorgen, dennoch verspricht der Lebensabend glücklich zu werden -- bis Fiona immer stärker unter Gedächtnisverlust leidet und man Alzheimer bei ihr diagnostiziert. Schon bald darauf beschließt sie, sich selbst in ein Pflegeheim, das auf Fälle wie ihren spezialisiert ist, einzuweisen. Zum ersten Mal in ihrer Ehe werden die beiden getrennt. Und eine altmodische Aufnahmebestimmung des Pflegeheims Meadowlake sieht vor, dass in den ersten 30 Tagen des Aufenthalts kein Angehöriger die Patienten besuchen darf, damit diese sich ungestört einleben können.

Als Grant seine Frau nach diesen 30, für ihn quälend langen Tagen erstmals besucht, erkennt Fiona ihn nicht wieder. Schlimmer noch, ihre ganze Zuneigung gehört jetzt vielmehr Aubrey (Michael Murphy), einem anderen Heimbewohner. Grant bleibt nichts anderes übrig, als seinen neuen Status als „Bekannter", der Fiona täglich besucht, zu akzeptieren. Als Aubrey jedoch eines Tages wieder von seiner Frau Marian (Oscar®-Gewinnerin Olympia Dukakis) nach Hause geholt wird und Fiona daraufhin in eine schwere Depression verfällt, erkennt Grant, dass ihm das größte Opfer an die gemeinsame Liebe noch bevorsteht ...

title: NBA 2K13: Block party + Swat and swipe (Fiesta en la zona + Sangre y sudor)
tags: ['Trophy', 'Trofeo', 'Achievement', 'Logro', 'NBA2K13', '2K13', 'NBA 2K13', 'Block party', 'Swat and swipe', 'Fiesta en la zona', 'Sangre y sudor', 'Machinima', 'Playstation 3']
description:
I did these with 2 controllers. Select a team with a good blocker (I chose Lakers 70-71 with Chamberlain), then assign that blocker to defend the smallest player of the other team. Play with that small player near the basket and don't select the blocker with the other controller, so the cpu will try to block shots automatically. When you have 10 blocks, trophy will pop up, then just steal 5 times with any player of the same team that did the 10 blocks.

Hice estos con dos mandos. Selecciona un equipo con un buen taponador (yo elegí los Lakers del 70-71 con Chamberlain), y asigna el taponador para que defienda al jugador más bajito del otro equipo. Juega con ese jugador bajito cerca de la canasta y no selecciones al taponador con el otro mando, de manera que la cpu intentará taponar automáticamente. Cuando hagas 10 tapones saltará el trofeo, y entonces sólo faltará hacer 5 robos con cualquier jugador del equipo que hizo los tapones.

description:
2015年2月4日（水）発売予定

“インディーズゾンビ映画史上、最高傑作！！！”

ゾンビが蔓延する終末世界を旅する凸凹コンビの末行く先を描いた
異色のゾンビホラー・ヒューマンドラマ・ロードムービー！

「ゾンビ映画特有の終末感を感じさせない」「これまでなかった変化球ゾンビ作品」と、世界各国のホラー映画祭で旋風を巻き起こした本作、満を持して日本上陸！！！

オランダ・アムステルダムファンタスティック映画祭　最優秀作品賞
スペイン・マラガファンタスティック国際映画祭　最優秀作品賞
カナダ・トロントアフターダーク映画祭　観客賞/脚本賞/音楽賞/美術賞
スペイン・シッチェス‐カタロニアン国際映画祭　最優秀作品賞ノミネート
ほか多数

■STORY■

ゾンビ達で溢れ荒廃した世界で生き残る野球大好きコンビのベンとミッキー。
どこかにあるはずの安楽の地を目指し、車で旅を続けていた。
一見お気楽なキャンプ旅行。時には釣りをし、気分転換にキャッチボールをする。
人家をみつけると、勝手に入り込んで食料や必要な物資を補給する。
そして時々、ゾンビと遭遇する他は誰にも出会わない…。

ゾンビ殺戮にも慣れて気ままな生活を楽しむ野性的なベンと、以前の平安な世界が恋しくてたまらない神経質なミッキー。ある日、たまたま拾ったトランシーバーの無線で、どこかに生存する女性の存在を知った二人はとった行動はー。

title: [TRAILER] The Housemaid - Jiyoung, Minho & Hara
description:
Kang Jiyoung is hired as a housemaid and nanny for a wealthy family. She is taken under the wing of the housekeeper Park Gyuri and takes care of the couple's young child while the wife Hara is heavily pregnant. Jiyoung is charmed upon meeting the husband Minho, who regularly travels abroad for business and is rarely home. Taking advantage of Jiyoung's naive presence, he begins an affair with her. 

Unsettled upon discovering them, Gyuri reports the affair to Minho's older sister Soonkyu, who then convinces Hara to take control of the situation. With Minho indifferent and Gyuri helpless, the cruel superiority of the upper-class manipulates Jiyoung to her psychological limit, leading to dark consequences.

Okay, so.............. a PG-15 trailer and fanfic idea? Yeah, I know, WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS TO INNOCENT JIYOUNG!?!? xD I was just browsing through an idea of mine when I rewatched Shinee and Kara's Juliette special stage, and I just thought to myself how cute Minho and Jiyoung would be. Then after that I went and watched the 2010 version of 'The Housemaid' and started to think which Kpop idols would be good as the characters, and BAM!! Seriously, the line-up in my head was so perfect, I had to write it down.

Now, you know if there's no link that means I haven't written it yet, but I just wanted to make a trailer first so that I can be motivated in future to write it. 

But please note: THIS ISN'T A LOVE STORY.

It'll be a "remake" like my Seungyeon-Onew 'Last Year at Kyoto Palace' of the French film 'Last Year at Marienbad' (which, damn me, I still haven't finished...). I was thinking pretty hard for the characters.

I have to honestly say, that although the movie Housemaid stuck with me and I feel fond of it, it wasn't really all that exciting. Sure, it was a Cannes Film Festival entry, and the trailer looked good, but not much excitement happened as it should've, the only thing that really satisfied me was the ending. Since this is an adult movie, I'm going to tone it down quite a bit for my readers (and maybe spice up the boring script...), but the main story will be the same. The trailer seems kind "steamy" at a point, but I seriously didn't know how else to portray an affair, and the song only helped so much. xD The original trailer had it as 'sensual suspense' and 'erotic thriller', which I SO beg to differ, but truth be told, the music controls the mood. 

For the characters, Jiyoung just matched the innocence and purity of the main female character so much, I immediately thought of her when I was watching the movie. For the housekeeper, even though she is played by a much older actress, I felt Gyuri was an awesome choice, since she has the right maturity and wisdom to be Jiyoung's guidance and voice of reason. I totally saw Minho and Hara in Lee Jungjae and Seowoo's roles, Minho with his cool, charismatic and superior player hotness (am still in love with Lee Jungjae from watching Il Mare), and Hara's ice-cold beauty with a childlike vulnerability just fell into place.

For Sunny, I never really intended to pick her because I'm not a SNSD fan, but I feel she is perfect. While in the movie it's the wife's mother, I felt if I made it out to be Hara's sister-in-law, hence Minho's sister, it'd have the same kind of connection, because the mother's relationship with the wife isn't really a maternal bond in the movie. Neither Nicole or Seungyeon seemed to fit the role, so I was thinking "If G7 were evil, who'd be the perfect choice?" And I picked Sunny, because the mother herself is classy, evil and calculating, but she does it to help teach her daughter how to protect herself and her family's reputation, no matter how cruelly and sadistically. If Sunny was evil, she'd be THAT kind of evil. xD

title: Mt Hood Summit, July 2008
tags: ['climbing', 'climb', 'mountaineering', 'Mt Hood', 'summit', 'Palmer', 'Portland', 'Oregon', 'Pearly Gates', 'Mazama shute', 'Hogsback', "Devil's Kitchen", 'Crater Rock', 'Timerberline Lodge']
description:
A small group of us summited Mt Hood in July 2008.

The adventure started at 10pm the night before. The weather had been horrible all week, and we were certain that conditions would not permit us to even try to climb. But we had nothing to lose just driving up to the trailhead at Timberline Lodge, so we packed up our stuff and headed to the mountain. Our entire commute to the mountain met with only rain...until the last 5 minutes. That is when we punched through the clouds during the final stretch of Timberline Rd.

We finally hit the trail around midnight. The sky was now absolutely clear and there was no wind, but there was a new moon, not ideal for a night climb. It was a long, quiet hike, only interrupted by the multiple snowcats grooming the slopes to the west. Headlamps were mandatory so our eyes never were able to adjust. Just as we reached the top of Palmer, a snowcat passed us to drop off its load of climbers who chose to skip the first 2 1/2 miles. They were fresh and full of energy, greatly contrasting our tired bodies and sore feet.

The rest of the climb included a beautiful sunrise, a constant stream of climbers, regularly dodging falling rocks (the result of climbing so late in the season), and unfortunately witnessing a significant fall by an unknown mountaineer.

It truly was a beautiful day!

title: 8/16 working fire Lewes Fire Dept.
description:
In the evening of 8/16/07 thunder storms began rolling in to the cape region.  With that, calls began pouring into the sussex county emergency operations center for various storm related calls in the east side of the county.
The first call of the night for the lewes volunteers was a carbon monoxide detector activation.  The on duty Engine crew staffed with 6 responded to this call in 82-5 along with the deputy chief who was duty officer for the evening.  Lewes volunteers kept additional crews in the station for any other emergencies.  10 minutes after the first emergency was dispatched a second emergency was dispatched for a working structure fire in Port Lewes. Engine 3 and Ladder 82 responded immediately from station 1 staffed with 9.  Ladder 82 was the first unit on scene with unit officer, Safety 82 reporting heavy fire from the roof area of side C of unit 91 & 92.   Command 82 and Engine 3 and Engine 5 arrived immediately thereafter with Deputy 82 assumed command.  Crews forced entry into both units and stretched a handline to each with the assistance of engine/tanker 4's crew.  Fire was found and quickly knocked down on the third floor. Mutual aid companies from milton indian river, and slaughter beach assisted on the scene and covering the 82 first due.  Special thanks to a local citizen for video of this incident.

title: LG Optimus 3D hands-on
description:
Glory be the LG Optimus 3D. Okay, we'll get right to it: the Optimus 3D is kinda kitschy, but at the same time fun, inevitable on a mobile device, and still a great conversation piece. The 4.3-inch glasses-free 3D display's effect in games, film, and even the UI is pretty convincing using the set's applied parallax barrier technology, which is otherwise unnoticeable while the effect is off. Best bit? You can film your own 3D videos using the dual cameras on the back then watch them on your 3D set via HDMI. The Optimus is by no means a tiny set, though, still pretty comfy when held. Material choices are top notch -- as we'd expect hope for in a high end device -- and as you'll see in the vid, it is plenty fast with no lag getting in the way of the little demo we had. So why not take a few minutes to admire the pics and videos (which unfortunately will be very flat for your eyes) won't you?
source: http://www.engadget.com/2011/02/14/lg-optimus-3d-hands-on/

title: 日々 / 吉田山田 / cover:伸[nobu] / Illustration：伸[nobu]
description:
今回は「吉田山田」さんの曲「日々」をリクエストを頂いていて歌わせて頂きました。「日々」は2014年8月27日発売の「吉田山田」の9枚目のシングルです。NHK「みんなのうた」のために書き下ろされたものです。老夫婦の何気ない日常を綴った曲ですが、これが「泣ける」と口コミで話題を呼び、NHKに問い合わせが殺到。シングル発売された12月から翌月にかけての放送でしたが、反響に応えて2月にも再度「みんなのうた」で放送されています。「みんなのうた」での曲の放送中に流れるアニメーションは、絵を描くのが趣味だという山田さんがキャラクターデザインを担当されていますが、今回は私「伸」のオリジナル･イラストでお楽しみ頂ければ幸いです。

初めて聴いてくださった方へ。
改めまして、はじめまして。伸(nobu)と言います。
私のページに来て下さり、有難う御座います。

私は数年前に「喉頭癌(声帯にできる癌)」を患い、声を失いかけました。
その１年前に初めての癌を患い、再発でした。
定期健診を欠かさなかったお陰で、比較的、初期の段階で発見され、
すぐに処置をして頂き助けて頂きました。
しかし、暫くの間、歌うどころか喋る事すらままならない状況になりました。
当時の私は、喋る事も仕事の一つだったため、それはとても辛く悲しかったですね…
もしかしたら、もう「声」と言うものには頼れないのでは？そう思いました。
声が出せなくたって目だって見える。耳だって聞こえる。体だって自由に動く。
何だって出来るじゃないか！
そう言い聞かせた時もありました。

医師の「ある程度までは声は戻るよ」と言う言葉を信じ
喉を使っても良いと言われてからは、リハビリをして
毎日、車の中で好きな曲を聴きながら声を出す練習をしました。
誰にも聞かれたく見られたくなかったんです。
だから車の中は僕のリハビリ室でした。

その甲斐あって、医師も驚くほどの回復をみせ、
現在では喋るだけでなく歌う事も出来るようになりました。
確かに、以前の自分の声ではなくなりましたし
１曲全てを声もかすれずに歌う事は難しいですが
でも、大好きな歌が歌えます。
友人の医師と支えてくれた周りの人達に感謝をしています。

そして2013年7月にまた、新たに疾患が見つかりました。
症例の少ない難病だと告げられ、同年10月には障害者となりました。
明日はどうなるか解りません。

「負けたら終わり ではなく あきらめたら終わり」
「笑って生きるも一日、泣いて生きるも一日、どうせなら笑顔で」
この二つは私の座右の銘です。

世の中には、色んな病や悩みなどと闘っている人達が沢山いると思います。
どうか諦めないで下さい。

私は大好きな歌を歌ってここに載せて行きます。
ここには沢山の歌の上手な方々が掲載されています。
私の歌はその方々には程遠いものです。
でも、ここまで歌えるようになりました。
良かったら聴いてみて下さい。
ありがとうございました。
伸(nobu)

title: game greats
description:
كيم كريت GAME GREATS
سوفه يتم افتتاح موقع كيم كريت قريباً ان شاء الله
موقع كيم كريت خامس موقع بالعالم من حيث التقنيه والتطورات كيم كريت يحمل المواصفات التاليه
-١-العب البلياردو
-٢-العب اون لاين
-٣-دردشة اثناء العب وخارج العب
-٤-+كامره +مايك+مواصفات ترفيه
-٥-يحمل السرعه العاليه والتقنيات
(قسم القروبات)
1-لا يستطيع المستخدم ان يعمل قروب اله بعد تجاوز 250 نقطه
2-عنده تجاوز 100 عضو مشترك بالقروب تحصل على روم مخفي لا يظهر بس امام اعضاء القروب خاص بك وبسم قروبك
3-توجد في كل قروب محادثه جماعيه خاصه لكل الاعضاء المشتركين بالقروب
4-مدير القروب يحصل على علامة خاصه وتظهر امام زوار الموقع وهذهي العلامة تكون خاصه بس للمدراء القروبات لكي يكون مميز
5-مدير القروب يقدر ان يضع مشرفين داخل روم القروب
6-مدير القروب من حقه ان يحذف مشترك او يمسح الجات او يضرب كنور(بلوك-حجب)
(قسم الزوار)
1-المستخدم لا يستطيع ان يتكلم خارج اللعبه اله بعد تجاوز( 5 نقاط )
2-توجد ميزات خاصه للنقاط 100 - 500 - 1000 - 5000 - 10000
كل ما زادت النقاط تزيد الميزات
3-المستخدم لا يستطيع ان يشترك بقروب اله بعد تجاوز ( 50 نقطه )
4-المستخدم يستطيع ان يضع صوره خاصه بهي في البروفايل
5-يوجد لكل مستخدم id ظاهري + id مخفي
6- الخ...
(قسم ميزات الموقع)
1-يوجد اضافة لون لكل اسم وهذا الون لهو ميزات وكل لون عن الاخر لهو ميزات تختلف
2-يستطيع 4 اشخاص العب على طاوله واحده ثنين ضد ثنين(زوجي)
3-كل ما تزود ( 20 نقطه )يتغير نوعية الكيوب(المضرب)
4-يوجد بالموقع كامره HD (كامره نوعية البلازمه)
5-يوجد بالموقع مايك بحدث التقنيات
الكامره+المايك-توجد في كل لعبة خاصه وخارج العبه وداخل الدردشة الفرديه وبكل مكان:))
6-توجد لكل لعبة خاصه بين ثنين ترقيم القيم مثلا رقم الطاوله 14
7-يوجد ساعه في كل الموقع
8-يوجد برايفت (كلام خاص بين ثنين) داخل العبه وخارج العبه
9-يوجد بالموقع محادثه خاصه لكل العرب+محاجثه لكل الاجانب
10-يوجد لكل دوله لها روم خاص محادثه +كامره+مايك فقط
11-يوجد في لعبة 8 بول- 7-7 بنط + 5-5 بنط+بنط عام
12-عندما تلعب قيم مع شخص يمكنك ان تسحب الصول او تقدمه او تنحي
13-يوجد بالموقع اضافة كصديق مثلا انت وصاحبك ممكن ان تضيفه كصديق
14-اسم المستخدم يتكون من 20 حرف فقط
15-تستطيع ان تكتب تحت الحساب او تحت الاسم الخاص بك ما تشاء مثلا انا مو هنا او طالع مع اصدقائي
16-كل ما تلعب 4 قيم فوز تحصل على نقطه
17-يوجد تصنيف خاص بكل لاعبين المميزين
18-يوجد في كل قائمة للمستخدم1-طلب لون اسم2-شكوى3-الخ...

title: Evento Apple Septiembre, LG Optimus L1 ll, BlackBerry Z30, HTC One Max, Android cuota de 40%
description:
PUESTO N° 5: Android eleva su cuota de mercado hasta el 80%

Ayer se publicaron los datos del estudio de mercado que IDC hace trimestralmente sobre smartphones, y los resultados siguen dando como ganador a Android. Hay varios datos importantes que vamos a analizar, pues no sólo el aumento de Android es reseñable.

Lo primero y más importante, en el segundo trimestre de 2013 se vendieron 236,4 millones de smartphones, de todos los fabricantes y sistemas operativos. Esto es un crecimiento brutal, pues en el mismo trimestre de 2012 se vendieron "sólo" 156,2 millones de terminales. Es decir, el mercado de los smartphones sigue creciendo.

MAS INFO: http://www.xatakandroid.com/mercado/android-eleva-su-cuota-de-mercado-hasta-el-80

PUESTO N° 4: Primera imagen oficial del HTC One Max, el nuevo phablet de HTC

Desde hace varios meses venimos escuchando rumores sobre un phablet de HTC, el cual se hace llamar HTC One Max dadas sus similitudes con su hermano menor, el HTC One. En un principio eran rumores con poca repercusión, pero conforme pasan los días y nos acercamos a la IFA 2013, estos se están intensificando hasta tal punto que ya tenemos la primera imagen del HTC One Max, filtrada gracias a la archiconocida cuenta de Twitter Evleaks.

MAS INFO: http://www.celularis.com/htc/imagen-htc-one-max/

PUESTO N° 3: Aparece un vídeo de la nueva BlackBerry Z30 con pantalla de 5 pulgadas

IFA 2013 está cerca, lo que significa que nos espera una semana masiva de lanzamientos de productos, siendo uno de los más esperados la nueva Blackberry Z30, el primer smartphone de la vieja RIM con pantalla de 5 pulgadas. Hasta hace pocos días, este dispositivo era un simple rumor que circulaba por la red, pero las sucesivas filtraciones y, sobre todo, el vídeo de BlackBerry Z30 que ha aparecido hoy en la red, confirman la existencia y el lanzamiento inminente de este nuevo smartphone de BlackBerry.

MAS INFO: http://www.celularis.com/blackberry/video-blackberry-z30/

PUESTO N° 2: LG Optimus L1 II

El LG Optimus L1 II tiene unas especificaciones muy básicas. Destaca una pantalla reducida, de 3 pulgadas de diámetro. La resolución es QVGA (320 × 240 pixels) y la pantalla es táctil capacitiva. Respecto al tamaño, es muy reducido: 102.9×59.2×12.2 mm.

El procesador que mueve el terminal es un chip Snapdragon MSM7225A single core a 1 GHz de velocidad, un procesador muy básico. La memoria RAM es de 512 MB. El almacenamiento es de 4 GB de memoria interna ampliable mediante tarjeta microSD. Un almacenamiento nada despreciable para la gama de la que estamos hablando.

MAS INFO: http://www.xatakandroid.com/moviles-android/lg-optimus-l1-ii-toda-la-informacion-del-nuevo-android-de-lg

PUESTO N° 1: Jim Dalrymple confirma la presentación del nuevo iPhone en el evento especial del 10 de Septiembre

Si hay algo casi tan definitivo como una invitación oficial de Apple para confirmar uno de sus eventos, esa es tres simples letras en boca de la persona adecuada: Jim Dalrymple de The Loop, probablemente uno de los pocos bloggers del mundo que puede presumir de tener linea directa con los chicos de Cupertino.
Un simple y escueto "Yep" (Sip) que sigue la tradición de Steve Jobs y que confirma con un 99% de probabilidad la frase que le precede, extraída del anuncio realizado ayer mismo por All Things Digital: Se espera que Apple presente su próximo iPhone en un evento especial el 10 de septiembre. Así que mientras esperamos la invitación oficial, ya podemos ir haciendo hueco en la agenda... habemus papam.

MAS INFO: http://www.applesfera.com/iphone/jim-dalrymple-confirma-la-presentacion-del-nuevo-iphone-en-el-evento-especial-del-10-de-septiembre

title: Mundo Nativo - Ecologia, Cultura e Lazer
tags: ['Mundo Nativo', 'Liberdade', 'Cultura', 'Rio Grande do Sul', 'RS', 'Gravataí', 'Tradicionalismo', 'Camping', 'Acampamento', 'Natureza', 'Ecologia', 'Nativismo', 'Escoteiros', 'Escotismo', 'Sustentabilidade', 'Vida', 'Lazer', 'Meio Ambiente', 'Felicidade', 'Preservação', 'Reserva', 'Reserva Ambiental', 'Atividades', 'Verde', 'Eventos', 'Família', 'Produtividade', 'Gaúcho', 'Gaudério', 'Rural', 'Pesquisa', 'Centro de Eventos', 'Educação', 'Educação Ambiental', 'Mundo', 'Nativo', 'Originalidade', 'Sonoridade', 'Culturalidade', 'Responsabilidade Social', 'Consciência', 'Comportamento', 'Projeto Pedagógico']
description:
O histórico do Mundo Nativo, teve origem em 1996 quando a área foi adquirida pela família Araújo Ranzolin tendo como objetivo num primeiro momento, ser espaço de convivência e de atividade produtiva rural, onde a família poderia se reunir nos finais de semana para realizar confraternizações, melhorias e manutenções na área, com trabalhos voltados a pecuária de corte. Este vínculo ligado as tradições é fruto da família Araújo, que perpassa gerações.

Durante, seguindo o legitimo acolhimento gaúcho, a família abriu sua propriedade nos finais de semana para amigos, parentes e conhecidos, o que se tornou um hábito familiar. As pessoas que visitavam a fazenda ficavam encantadas com a beleza do lugar, e perguntavam por que a família Araújo Ranzolin não criava um espaço para promover eventos, então surgiu pela primeira vez à ideia de criar um centro de eventos para receber empresas ou associações, que buscavam um espaço de lazer e recreação em contato com a natureza, então esta ideia começou a ser maturada pela família.

A primeira iniciativa enquanto evento social, foi realizada através da Casa das Gaxetas, empresa co-ligada da propriedade, em 2001 foi organizada a festa de final de ano a FESCON - Festa de Confraternização. O evento foi um sucesso, todos os convidados, dentre eles clientes, amigos, fornecedores, colaboradores e diretores, gostaram muito do espaço, e os comentários foram vinculados à beleza local, e questionavam porque não se fazia em centro de eventos deste local.

Então em 2001, a propriedade consolidou sua organização em atividades em Turismo Rural, mas também deu continuidade a pecuária de corte, uma vez que já tinha estrutura para manejo de gado e lidas campeiras.

No inicio a gestão era realizada por Ramiro Araújo que organizava a parte comercial e divulgação, e a família ajudava na operacionalização dos eventos. Atualmente, a família trabalha na organização dos eventos maiores, distribuída em agendamento, recepção, alimentação e organização e manutenção em geral.

O Centro de Eventos e Lazer num primeiro momento foi denominado Fazendinha que buscava fomento na tradição gaúcha, e nas lidas campeiras, através do Piquete de Laçadores "Amizade e Tradição", sua referência, pois acreditava que esta cultura regional deveria ser mantida, preservada e polinizada enquanto história do Rio Grande do Sul.

A Fazendinha tinha também como objetivo organizar eventos programados, tendo como foco em aniversários, retiros, empresariais, tiro de laço.

Porém com o intuito de ampliar as atividades em comprometimento sócio-ambiental, a Fazendinha abre suas "porteiras" com o objetivo para receber instituições de ensino, buscando ressignificar e complementar a ações vinculadas a sala de aula, através da criação de um Projeto Pedagógico- PP para ampliar, fortalecer, qualificar e diversificar as vivências enquanto complemento escolar, empresarial ou em comportamentos humanos.

Neste intento, foi convidada a prof. Mestre em Educação PUCRS Rozimeri Pereira Ranzolin, que elaborou o Projeto Pedagógico buscando criar vivências de contato direto com a natureza bem como cenários interventivos que encaminhem consciência em Educação Ambiental, contará com uma equipe interdisciplinar que estabelecerá conexões estéticas e bioéticas.

Durante o processo de ideação do PP, surgiu a necessita da alteração do nome Fazendinha, pois havia outra proposta institucional que não unicamente um Centro de Eventos, mas um projeto em Educação Ambiental, então foi repensado um nome novo que daria conta e uma nova proposta, então após pesquisas, estudos, análises e discussões o nome MUNDO NATIVO nome escolhido pela equipe de gestão, por encontrar nele a abrangência, originalidade, sonoridade, culturalidade, enfim a intencionalidade que movimenta a empresa enquanto responsabilidade social em Ecologia, Cultura e Lazer.

title: An exciting and colorful Cirque du Monde gathering - Cirque du Soleil
tags: ['Cirque du Monde', 'Cirque du Soleil', 'Grand rassemblement', 'Global Citizenship', 'Social Circus', 'Cirque', 'du', 'Soleil', 'Circo', 'del', 'Sol', 'Circus', 'Arts', 'Performing']
description:
Learn more about Cirque du Soleil here: http://cirk.me/11Ut74X
Learn more about Cirque du Monde here: http://cirk.me/11UtbBJ
On May 28, as part of the 15th anniversary celebrations of Cirque du Monde, more than 150 young participants from Quebec descended on Cirque du Soleil's headquarters in Montreal to take part in three days of festivities, exchanges and circus arts! 

For 15 years, Cirque du Monde has worked to make moments like these happen for young people; moments when creativity, team spirit, pride and achievement take over from the troubles they face on a daily basis. 

Apprenez en plus sur le Cirque du Soleil ici: http://cirk.me/11Ut74X
Apprenez en plus sur le Cirque du Monde ici: http://cirk.me/11UtbBJ
Le 28 Mai, pour le 15ème anniversaire du Cirque du Monde, plus 150 jeunes participants de Quebec sont descendu au siège social du Cirque du Soleil a Montréal pour faire partie de trois jours de festivité, d'échange et de cirque!

Pendant 15 ans, le Cirque du Monde a travaille dur afin de créer des moments tels que ceux ci pour les jeunes: des moments ou la créativité, l'esprit d'équipe, la fierté et l'accomplissement deviennent plus forts que les problèmes qu'ils rencontrent chaque jour.

title: Wind River Rafting Trip - Wet Planet Whitewater
description:
One of the most challenging commercial rafting runs in the Pacific Northwest, the Wind River cascades through tightly spaced boulder gardens and steep ledge drops in a series of class IV to class V rapids. Wet Planet guests will participate with guides in scouting and portaging while running rapids such as Initiation, Rams Horn, and Climax Falls. Set in a deep canyon, spectacular waterfalls, towering cliffs, and strange clay walls create an unforgettable atmosphere for a spectacular trip. This all day trip includes a hot riverside lunch and is the perfect run for experienced paddlers seeking the next level of adventure.
Join Wet Planet - the center for whitewater Rafting & Kayaking in Washington and Oregon - on the Wind River.
